ile an image is loading or a Failure image if the transfer is unsuccessful. The Failure image can also be customised to any SF system image."}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ImageDataPickerView","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/imagedatapicker\/imagedatapickerview","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ImageDataPickerView","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"ImageDataPickerView"},"doc://com.technistic.ImageDataPicker/documentation/ImageDataPicker":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","title":"ImageDataPicker","abstract":[{"text":"A Framework for binding an Image to SwiftData with a control that allows you to select a photo from the PhotoLibrary using the PhotosUI ","type":"text"},{"code":"PhotosPicker","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/imagedatapicker","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.technistic.ImageDataPicker\/documentation\/ImageDataPicker"}}}